 is applied to field data, where similar\nresults to synthetic data are achieved, which shows the potential for the\napplication on real data signals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jan 2019 17:32:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-12"}
