erforms the AF based\nEHB-OPS-RS and such an outage advantage becomes more significant, as the number\nof EH relays increases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jan 2019 18:08:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 May 2019 08:53:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 8 Oct 2019 04:10:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-09"}
